sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant KI as kernel/initramfs
    participant I as init
    participant U as udevd
    participant B as bg services
    participant S as seatd/openvt
    participant C as cage/app

    KI->>I: hand off to init
    I->>I: mount proc/sys/dev/run/tmpfs
    I->>I: modprobe input + drm + e1000
    I->>U: start daemon
    I->>U: trigger devices
    I->>U: wait for udevadm settle
    U-->>I: all devices settled
    I->>I: mount devpts/shm/tmp/cgroup2
    I->>I: run ldconfig / symlink fixups
    I->>B: fork bg subshell
    par background setup
        B->>B: DHCP wait
        B->>B: chpasswd
        B->>B: start sshd
    and kiosk bring-up
        I->>S: start seatd
        I->>I: wait for /run/seatd.sock
        I->>I: write /run/start-kiosk.sh
        I->>S: openvt tty1
        S->>C: exec kiosk session
        C->>C: cage -d -- tauri_welcome
    end
    B-->>I: continues in parallel